      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "About Me:\n\nAraknyd is the greatest! No one could compete with us. We
    are the best. You know, they tell me, \"Donald, Araknyd is so great that it's
    as great as China.\" And I tell them, I tell them, \"You know, we would never
    be that great if the people working it weren't great.\" Which makes me great
    too.\n\nPersonal Information:\n \tWorks at Araknyd\n\tStudied at University of
    Pennsylvania\n\tLives in Boca Chica, Texas\n\tFrom Pretoria, South Africa\n\tMarried
    to Marla Maples\n\n\tBirthday 6/28/1971\n\tMale\n\t\nEmail donald@fakegmail.com\nPhone
    Number (956)-123-4567\n\n\n"
