  m_text: 'Post

    5/25/2026 at 2:43am



    OBAMA could never have a happier
    family. We know this. He knows this. My son Donald Musk Jr. has told me that
    no family could be happier. And others will tell you that we aren''t happy and
    they are wrong. Losers. That''s what I call them, LOSERS! But not me, Donny.
    I could never be a loser because Araknyd is great so I am great.

'
